  "detailed_description": "No tedious grinding, just pure Boss Fight! Challenge yourself in this fast-paced battle with different builds and break new high scores!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/1185353bd5dfcc25b871c00bff5bc890.poster.avif?t=1754928484\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/1185353bd5dfcc25b871c00bff5bc890.webm?t=1754928484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/1185353bd5dfcc25b871c00bff5bc890.mp4?t=1754928484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Combat System</h2>Combine 2 types of invocation to produce different spells. Each spell has it's own pros and cons and is upgradable via the Talent Tree.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/ad318a19bb8b9c0954a99cc06fa62996.poster.avif?t=1754928484\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/ad318a19bb8b9c0954a99cc06fa62996.webm?t=1754928484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/ad318a19bb8b9c0954a99cc06fa62996.mp4?t=1754928484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Experiment with each combination and utilize them for different scenarios.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/0360e2fe40d05f732e4cf9c95a0151b0.poster.avif?t=1754928484\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/0360e2fe40d05f732e4cf9c95a0151b0.webm?t=1754928484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/0360e2fe40d05f732e4cf9c95a0151b0.mp4?t=1754928484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Charge up your special bar and bring forth your ultimate spells!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/b4b6c071f2f2bde12934e7b1471e737b.poster.avif?t=1754928484\" width=600 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/b4b6c071f2f2bde12934e7b1471e737b.webm?t=1754928484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/b4b6c071f2f2bde12934e7b1471e737b.mp4?t=1754928484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/c594dc7075067f667c88a94ff6df3d29.poster.avif?t=1754928484\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/c594dc7075067f667c88a94ff6df3d29.webm?t=1754928484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/c594dc7075067f667c88a94ff6df3d29.mp4?t=1754928484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize your talents</h2>Utilize your free skill points and come up with your own unique builds!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935380/extras/4cba9330414e666146d5f5661ca5b20a.poster.avif?t=1754928484\" width=600 height=146 ><source sr